These are Puzzles for 2x7 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-2-1::.
There are 7 different nationalities: australian, french, indonesian, italian, japanese, thai, turkish
7 different games are played: mah-jongg, whist, scrabble, billiard, canasta, bridge, go
 1. the australian is between the italian and the turkish##2
 2. the french is in the middle##1
 3. the person playing canasta is on the right of the person playing go##1
 4. the japanese is between the person playing scrabble and the person playing canasta##2
 5. the person playing whist is on the right of the person playing bridge##1
 6. the person playing whist is on the right of the italian##1
 7. the person playing mah-jongg is between the person playing billiard and the person playing scrabble##2
 8. the person playing whist is on the left of the turkish##1
 9. the japanese is on the left of the thai##1
10. the japanese is on the right of the person playing scrabble##1
11. the thai is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2      |    3    |     4     |     5      |     6      |    7    |
| Nationality   | italian | australian | turkish | french    | indonesian | japanese   | thai    |
| Game         | bridge  | whist   | billiard | mah-jongg | scrabble   | go | canasta |

