.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-2-2::.
There 7 different types of food: apple, cauliflower, grapefruit, grapes, lettuce, pomegranate, pumpkin
The people perfer 7 different movie-genres: fantasy, martial-arts, action, zombie, crime, comedy, sports
1. the person watching comedy movies is on the far left##1
2. the person eating grapefruit is between the person eating pomegranate and the person watching comedy movies##2
3. the person watching martial-arts movies is on the right of the person watching fantasy movies##1
4. the person eating pumpkin is on the right of the person watching action movies##1
5. the person eating cauliflower is in the middle##1
6. the person watching crime movies is on the left of the person watching fantasy movies##1
7. the person watching sports movies is on the left of the person eating cauliflower##1
8. the person eating lettuce is on the left of the person watching zombie movies##1
9. the person eating grapes is on the right of the person watching fantasy movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2      |      3      |      4      |    5    |     6      |    7    |
| Food          | lettuce | grapefruit | pomegranate | cauliflower | pumpkin | apple      | grapes  |
| Movie-Genre   | comedy | zombie  | sports     | action     | crime  | fantasy | martial-arts |

