.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-2-3::.
The people have 7 different hobbies: filmmaking, gardening, magic-tricks, board-games, hiking, sudoku, chess
7 different pets are kept: fish, goat, hamster, pony, rabbit, rat, turtle
 1. the person who's hobby is hiking is on the left of the person who's hobby is filmmaking##1
 2. the owner of the hamster is on the left of the owner of the pony##1
 3. the owner of the rabbit is the person who's hobby is chess##1
 4. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is on the left of the person who's hobby is sudoku##1
 5. the owner of the fish is on the left of the owner of the turtle##1
 6. the person who's hobby is board-games is the owner of the pony##1
 7. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is on the left of the owner of the hamster##1
 8. the owner of the fish is between the owner of the turtle and the person who's hobby is board-games##2
 9. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is on the right of the owner of the rat##1
10. the person who's hobby is gardening is in the middle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2    |    3     |    4    |   5    |   6    |     7     |
| Hobby   | chess | hiking | filmmaking | gardening   | board-games | magic-tricks | sudoku |
| Pet           | rabbit | rat     | goat     | hamster | pony   | fish   | turtle    |

