.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-2-4::.
There are 7 different favourite beverages: fanta, iced-tea, juice, lemonade, sprite, tea, water
The people grow 7 different varities of flowers: begonia, tulip, lily, amaryllis, daffodil, dahlia, daisy
 1. the person drinking water is on the left of the person who growslily##1
 2. the person drinking sprite is on the right of the person who growsdaffodil##1
 3. the person who growsdahlia is on the right of the person who growsamaryllis##1
 4. the person drinking sprite is on the right of the person who growsdaffodil##1
 5. the person who growsbegonia is on the right of the person drinking fanta##1
 6. the person who growsamaryllis is between the person drinking juice and the person who growsdahlia##2
 7. the person drinking fanta is in the middle##1
 8. the person who growsamaryllis is on the left of the person drinking lemonade##1
 9. the person drinking iced-tea is the person who growstulip##1
10. the person who growsbegonia is the person drinking water##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |     3     |   4    |     5      |     6     |    7     |
| Beverage      | juice    | sprite  | lemonade  | fanta  | water      | tea       | iced-tea |
| Flower   | daffodil | amaryllis | dahlia | daisy | begonia | lily | tulip  |

