.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-2-5::.
The people prefer 7 different types of sport: weightlifting, baseball, handball, rowing, skiing, swimming, skateboarding
The people use 7 different means of transport: bike, helicopter, motorbike, ship, skateboard, train, van
1. the person driving the ship is on the right of the person driving the skateboard##1
2. the person driving the skateboard is the person who's sport is baseball##1
3. the person driving the bike is between the person who's sport is skateboarding and the person who's sport is weightlifting##2
4. the person who's sport is swimming is on the right of the person driving the skateboard##1
5. the person driving the bike is in the middle##1
6. the person driving the train is on the left of the person who's sport is weightlifting##1
7. the person driving the motorbike is on the left of the person driving the skateboard##1
8. the person driving the helicopter is the person who's sport is rowing##1
9. the person who's sport is skiing is the person driving the train##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |   2   |     3     |  4   |     5     |     6      |  7   |
| Sport   | rowing      | skiing | weightlifting | handball | skateboarding      | baseball      | swimming |
| Transport     | helicopter | train | van       | bike | motorbike | skateboard | ship |

