.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-2-7::.
7 different pets are kept: frog, guinea-pig, horse, goldfish, dog, lizard, fish
The people prefer 7 different types of sport: cricket, cycling, parkour, rowing, rugby, surfing, volleyball
 1. the person who's sport is surfing is the owner of the dog##1
 2. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the left of the person who's sport is volleyball##1
 3. the person who's sport is cycling is in the middle##1
 4. the owner of the horse is between the person who's sport is rugby and the person who's sport is volleyball##2
 5. the person who's sport is cricket is on the left of the owner of the goldfish##1
 6. the owner of the frog is on the left of the person who's sport is cricket##1
 7. the person who's sport is rowing is the owner of the frog##1
 8. the owner of the lizard is the person who's sport is rugby##1
 9. the person who's sport is parkour is between the person who's sport is rugby and the owner of the dog##2
10. the owner of the horse is on the left of the owner of the lizard##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1    |    2    |       3       |    4    |    5     |    6    |    7     |
| Pet   | frog | guinea-pig    | goldfish | horse   | lizard | fish    | dog |
| Sport      | rowing | cricket | volleyball    | cycling | rugby    | parkour | surfing  |

