.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-2-9::.
The people's birthday is in 7 different months: june, may, february, october, november, april, december
The people use 7 different means of transport: bus, motorbike, quad-bike, skateboard, taxi, tram, trike
1. the person who's birthday is in june is the person driving the tram##1
2. the person driving the motorbike is on the left of the person who's birthday is in june##1
3. the person who's birthday is in november is between the person driving the trike and the person driving the taxi##2
4. the person who's birthday is in may is on the left of the person who's birthday is in october##1
5. the person driving the bus is in the middle##1
6. the person who's birthday is in november is on the left of the person who's birthday is in february##1
7. the person driving the skateboard is on the left of the person driving the taxi##1
8. the person who's birthday is in november is on the right of the person who's birthday is in april##1
9. the person driving the trike is on the right of the person who's birthday is in november##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |   3    |    4    |    5     |     6     |   7    |
| Birthday   | may | october     | april | november | february | december  | june |
| Transport     | quad-bike | skateboard | taxi   | bus     | trike    | motorbike | tram   |

