The people's birthday is in 7 different months: october, may, april, march, july, february, august
1. the person who's birthday is in february is the person drinking cola##1
2. the person drinking 7up is on the right of the person drinking coffee##1
3. the person who's birthday is in april is on the right of the person drinking coffee##1
4. the person who's birthday is in february is between the person who's birthday is in march and the person who's birthday is in may##2
5. the person who's birthday is in august is on the left of the person who's birthday is in april##1
6. the person who's birthday is in march is on the far right##1
7. the person drinking tea is on the right of the person drinking 7up##1
8. the person drinking fanta is between the person drinking milk and the person who's birthday is in february##2
9. the person who's birthday is in july is on the right of the person who's birthday is in october##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |     2     |      3      |      4       |    5    |      6      |    7    |
| Beverage   | coffee  | 7up       | tea         | milk         | fanta   | cola        | mirinda |
| Birthday      | august | april | october | july | may | february | march  |

